{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.1","label":"","reference":"2 Thessaloniciens 3:1","prev_osis_id":"2Thess.002.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Thess.003.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Exhortation \u00e0 prier pour les progr\u00e8s de l\u2019\u00c9vangile, \u00e0 s\u2019\u00e9loigner de ceux qui vivent dans le d\u00e9sordre, et \u00e0 travailler paisiblement<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-5: cf. (Col 4:3, 4. Ro 15:30-32.) 1 Co 1:8, 9. Ja 5:7, 8.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Thess.3.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Au reste, fr\u00e8res, priez pour nous, afin que la parole du Seigneur se r\u00e9pande et soit glorifi\u00e9e comme elle l\u2019est chez-vous,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Thess.3","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.3.2","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 3:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.2.17","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 2:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.2.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.2","label":"","reference":"2 Thessaloniciens 3:2","prev_osis_id":"2Thess.003.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Thess.003.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Thess.3.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>et afin que nous soyons d\u00e9livr\u00e9s des hommes m\u00e9chants et pervers; car tous n\u2019ont pas la foi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Thess.3","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.3.3","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 3:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.3.1","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 3:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.3","label":"","reference":"2 Thessaloniciens 3:3","prev_osis_id":"2Thess.003.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Thess.003.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Thess.3.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Le Seigneur est fid\u00e8le, il vous affermira et vous pr\u00e9servera du malin.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Thess.3","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.3.4","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 3:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.3.2","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 3:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.4","label":"","reference":"2 Thessaloniciens 3:4","prev_osis_id":"2Thess.003.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Thess.003.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Thess.3.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Nous avons \u00e0 votre \u00e9gard cette confiance dans le Seigneur que vous faites et que vous ferez les choses que nous recommandons.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Thess.3","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.3.5","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 3:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.3.3","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 3:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.5","label":"","reference":"2 Thessaloniciens 3:5","prev_osis_id":"2Thess.003.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Thess.003.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Thess.3.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Que le Seigneur dirige vos c\u0153urs vers l\u2019amour de Dieu et vers la patience de Christ!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Thess.3","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.3.6","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 3:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.3.4","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 3:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.6","label":"","reference":"2 Thessaloniciens 3:6","prev_osis_id":"2Thess.003.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Thess.003.007,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 6-15: cf. 1 Th 2:9, 10; 4:1, 11, 12.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Thess.3.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>\n    nous vous recommandons, fr\u00e8res, au nom de notre Seigneur J\u00e9sus-Christ, de vous \u00e9loigner de tout fr\u00e8re qui vit dans le d\u00e9sordre, et non selon les instructions que vous avez re\u00e7ues de nous.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Thess.3","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.3.7","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 3:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.3.5","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 3:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.7","label":"","reference":"2 Thessaloniciens 3:7","prev_osis_id":"2Thess.003.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Thess.003.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Thess.3.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Vous savez vous-m\u00eames comment il faut nous imiter, car nous n\u2019avons pas v\u00e9cu parmi vous dans le d\u00e9sordre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Thess.3","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.3.8","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 3:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.3.6","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 3:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.8","label":"","reference":"2 Thessaloniciens 3:8","prev_osis_id":"2Thess.003.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Thess.003.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Thess.3.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Nous n\u2019avons mang\u00e9 gratuitement le pain de personne; mais, dans le travail et dans la peine, nous avons \u00e9t\u00e9 nuit et jour \u00e0 l\u2019\u0153uvre, pour n\u2019\u00eatre \u00e0 charge \u00e0 aucun de vous.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Thess.3","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.3.9","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 3:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.3.7","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 3:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.9","label":"","reference":"2 Thessaloniciens 3:9","prev_osis_id":"2Thess.003.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Thess.003.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Thess.3.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Ce n\u2019est pas que nous n\u2019en eussions le droit, mais nous avons voulu vous donner en nous-m\u00eames un mod\u00e8le \u00e0 imiter.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Thess.3","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.3.10","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 3:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.3.8","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 3:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.10","label":"","reference":"2 Thessaloniciens 3:10","prev_osis_id":"2Thess.003.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Thess.003.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Thess.3.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Car, lorsque nous \u00e9tions chez vous, nous vous disions express\u00e9ment: Si quelqu\u2019un ne veut pas travailler, qu\u2019il ne mange pas non plus.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Thess.3","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.3.11","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 3:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.3.9","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 3:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.11","label":"","reference":"2 Thessaloniciens 3:11","prev_osis_id":"2Thess.003.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Thess.003.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Thess.3.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Nous apprenons, cependant, qu\u2019il y en a parmi vous quelques-uns qui vivent dans le d\u00e9sordre, qui ne travaillent pas, mais qui s\u2019occupent de futilit\u00e9s.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Thess.3","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.3.12","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 3:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.3.10","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 3:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.12","label":"","reference":"2 Thessaloniciens 3:12","prev_osis_id":"2Thess.003.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Thess.003.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Thess.3.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Nous invitons ces gens-l\u00e0, et nous les exhortons par le Seigneur J\u00e9sus-Christ, \u00e0 manger leur propre pain, en travaillant paisiblement.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Thess.3","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.3.13","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 3:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.3.11","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 3:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.13","label":"","reference":"2 Thessaloniciens 3:13","prev_osis_id":"2Thess.003.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Thess.003.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Thess.3.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Pour vous, fr\u00e8res, ne vous lassez pas de faire le bien.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Thess.3","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.3.14","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 3:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.3.12","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 3:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.14","label":"","reference":"2 Thessaloniciens 3:14","prev_osis_id":"2Thess.003.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Thess.003.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Thess.3.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Et si quelqu\u2019un n\u2019ob\u00e9it pas \u00e0 ce que nous disons par cette lettre, notez-le, et n\u2019ayez point de communication avec lui, afin qu\u2019il \u00e9prouve de la honte.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Thess.3","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.3.15","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 3:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.3.13","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 3:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.15","label":"","reference":"2 Thessaloniciens 3:15","prev_osis_id":"2Thess.003.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Thess.003.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Thess.3.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Ne le regardez pas comme un ennemi, mais avertissez-le comme un fr\u00e8re.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Thess.3","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.3.16","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 3:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.3.14","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 3:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.16","label":"","reference":"2 Thessaloniciens 3:16","prev_osis_id":"2Thess.003.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Thess.003.017,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Salutation<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 16-18: cf. 2 Co 13:11-13.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Thess.3.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>\n    Que le Seigneur de la paix vous donne lui-m\u00eame la paix en tout temps, de toute mani\u00e8re! Que le Seigneur soit avec vous tous!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Thess.3","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.3.17","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 3:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.3.15","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 3:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.17","label":"","reference":"2 Thessaloniciens 3:17","prev_osis_id":"2Thess.003.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Thess.003.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Thess.3.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Je vous salue, moi Paul, de ma propre main. C\u2019est l\u00e0 ma signature dans toutes mes lettres; c\u2019est ainsi que j\u2019\u00e9cris.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Thess.3","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.3.18","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 3:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.3.16","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 3:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.18","label":"","reference":"2 Thessaloniciens 3:18","prev_osis_id":"2Thess.003.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Tim.001.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Thess.3.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Que la gr\u00e2ce de notre Seigneur J\u00e9sus-Christ soit avec vous tous!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Thess.3","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 3","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Tim.1.1","name":"1 Timoth\u00e9e 1:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Tim.1.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Thess.3.17","name":"2 Thessaloniciens 3:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Thess.3.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fc53d34b4.73488236');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fc53d34b4.73488236\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fc53d34b4.73488236","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fc53d34b4.73488236'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fc53d34b4.73488236\" height=\"1\